<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | Shouvair</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #aecfde, #d0bbe5);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a29ada, #926de2);
            color: #070707;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #080808;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            color: #0c0b0b;
        }

        .team {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .team-member {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #d1cfdb, #ccbade);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            width: 300px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .team-member:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .team-member img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border: 3px solid #f6f6f5;
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            color: #0a0a0a;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #0e0d0d;
        }

        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6A5ACD, #9370DB);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 20px 20px 0 0;
        }

        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background-color: #faf9f5;
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background-color: #f8f7f5;
            color: #000;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .team {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .team-member {
                width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
    <section>
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
            Welcome to <strong>Shouvair</strong>, your one-stop destination for premium fashion and timeless style. We bring together a curated collection of clothing essentials, from polos and shirts to dresses, bags, and accessories, all designed to reflect elegance and individuality. Our mission is simple: to deliver confidence through style.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
            At Shouvair, we believe fashion is more than just clothing — it’s a form of self-expression.
            Our vision is to create a platform where every individual can discover their unique style and feel confident in what they wear, turning everyday outfits into statements.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            WWe are dedicated to offering high-quality fashion products that combine comfort, style, and affordability. 
            Whether it’s a classic polo, a modern dress, or essential accessories, <strong>Shouvair</strong> makes it easy to explore, choose, and elevate your wardrobe — all in one place.
        </p>
    </section>
</div>


        <!-- Meet the Team Section -->
        <section>
            <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
            <div class="team">
                <div class="team-member">
                  
                    <h3>Dhruv Kundrai</h3>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                   
                    <h3>Aarya Rishi</h3>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                   
                    <h3>Aarav Shourie</h3>
                    
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                   
                    <h3>Advitya Hans</h3>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Shouvair. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="back-button">Back to Home</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
